data.description: Live TALL in your dream home in the heart of Kirkwood, Atlanta GA! This vibrant and spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven is more than just a houseCoit's a lifestyle. Nestled in the highly sought-after Kirkwood neighborhood, this residence offers the perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that dances through the large windows, casting a warm and inviting glow on the beautifully crafted hardwood floors. The open-concept living and dining areas create an ideal space for entertaining friends and family, while the gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage for the culinary enthusiast. One of the standout features of this property is the attached mother-in-law suite or separate apartment, presenting an incredible opportunity for additional income. Whether you choose to host guests in style or generate rental income, this versatile space adds an extra layer of functionality to an already impressive home.  Don't miss the chance to make this Kirkwood gem your own! Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and income potential in the heart of Atlanta. Your dream home awaits!
